These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: purple, amber, yellow, black, orange, white, apricot
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, old-henry, bolivar, oliveros, blend, fonseca, havana
 1. the person who likes purple is between the person who likes black and the person who likes apricot##2
 2. the person who likes amber is in the middle##1
 3. the blend-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 4. the person who likes orange is between the bolivar-smoker and the blend-smoker##2
 5. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
 6. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person who likes black##1
 7. the swisher-smoker is between the oliveros-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##2
 8. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 9. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes white##1
10. the person who likes orange is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
11. the person who likes white is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Color   | black | purple | apricot | amber    | yellow | orange   | white    |
| Cigar         | fonseca  | old-henry   | oliveros | swisher | bolivar   | havana | blend |

