.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, bongani, siglo, montecristo, baccarat, blend, old-henry
House: futuristic, art-deco, modern, farmhouse, colonial, victorian, cottage
1. the victorian house is on the far left##1
2. the siglo-smoker is between the blend-smoker and the victorian house##2
3. the art-deco house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the modern house##1
5. the bongani-smoker is in the middle##1
6. the colonial house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
7. the cottage house is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
8. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
9. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Cigar          | baccarat | siglo | blend | bongani | old-henry | swisher      | montecristo  |
| House   | victorian | farmhouse  | cottage     | modern     | colonial  | futuristic | art-deco |

