.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There 7 different types of food: radish, artichoke, pineapple, carrot, kiwi, peach, pepper
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: horror, action, scientific, drama, documentary, fantasy, sports
 1. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 2. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is between the person eating pineapple and the person watching fantasy movies##2
 7. the person eating radish is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
 9. the person eating artichoke is the person watching action movies##1
10. the person watching horror movies is the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Food      | pineapple    | kiwi  | carrot  | radish  | pepper      | peach       | artichoke |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | drama | fantasy | sports | horror | scientific | action  |

