.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
7 different pets are kept: snake, guinea-pig, fish, mouse, hamster, chinchilla, ferret
7 different games are played: canasta, whist, scrabble, monopoly, chess, go, mah-jongg
1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing chess is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the person playing canasta is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the snake##2
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person playing chess##1
5. the person playing canasta is in the middle##1
6. the person playing go is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
7. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing chess##1
8. the person playing whist is the owner of the mouse##1
9. the owner of the hamster is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Pet   | mouse      | hamster | snake | fish | ferret      | guinea-pig      | chinchilla |
| Game     | whist | go | mah-jongg       | canasta | scrabble | chess | monopoly |

