 6. the pakistani is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is the pakistani##1
 8. the australian is the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person playing billiard is between the person playing monopoly and the italian##2
10. the mexican is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | brazilian    | dutch | mexican   | australian | japanese    | italian |
| Game      | scrabble | backgammon | snooker    | bridge | monopoly    | billiard | whist  |

